<item>
            <title>[SOLR-2576] DirectSolrSpellChecker is not returning frequency information</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2576</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;DirectSolrSpellChecker is not returning frequency information.  This also causes the &quot;correctlySpelled&quot; flag in extended results to sometimes be wrong.  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
